                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On June 6, 1949, the Senate Committee on Foreign Relations unanimously agreed to
                    report the North Atlantic Treaty to the Senate for favorable action. For text of
                    the Committee’s report, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>,
                    June 19, 1949, page 787.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
